values:
its too often that i calm that i havent posted in a while. this is certainly the case.

but where else can i go to relive the tightly compacted, over worked, shit storm of a  muscle i call my brain.

and its always over a girl. 

i hate myself for it.

why cant i just grab her by the waist-side and go in for the kill?

why am i even thinking about this?

a week ago i forgot she even existed... now im losing sleep over her.

maybe its the way i think she looks at me, or the way my name just rolls of her tongue when she calls... its almost like she can see right into me; past my humorous defense mechanism and my awkward talking points. looking at my very essence, what ever that could be.

this super woman, with the power to make me melt with a single glance...

i set myself up so that i would never see or hear from her again... i just couldnt take it anymore, the rejection.

and i couldnt just be a friend... so i did what ive always done. shut myself out, i acted stupid, ignorant, jealous.

but after 6 months of complete radio silence, she had to pop up again. and.and... remind me of why i had a crush on her in the first place... 

best part is. i cant stop thinking about her.

fate has made it clear that i can not avoid this woman any longer. but romanticizing the very thot of us really being meant to be, makes me... nervous.

i clam up. forget how to use words. and looking into those bright eyes of hers is absolutely out of the question.

damnit... im falling apart at the seams... only she can do this too me. my kryptonite.

this is never going to happen, but wouldnt it be nice if it did?

if she even felt a fraction of how i feel about her... i think she would explode with love.

i am powerless, i am worried, i am tired.

its always a girl... this girl in particular.

Im done waiting around for any body.
For now one its "with or without you"
I will not be stepped on anymore over someone elses expence

Posted via LiveJournal.app.

independence day.

the closer it gets to july fourth, the closer i get to declaring my independence from the studio.

how poetic.

will it happen, maybe. its really just a matter of time.

As i lie awake with the internet as my only comfort i realize that im reaching yet another turning point in my life. What is this point in question? I need to change careers. Its sad yet oh soo true. My heart is not in it anymore. I cannot drone away infront of the computer no longer.

It is said; if you do what you love you will never work a day in your life. This not always the case. Ive been a graphic designer for 3 years now. I dont know if i have another 3 left in me. Being creative is what im best at but it was always been more of a past time for me. My creative integrety is being tested every day i step foot into that office. And for what? A paycheck? Now this past time is a means to survive? This use to be fun. Now its all being sucked away. I must be crazy. Most of my college friends dont even have jobs yet. I should be so lucky. But its not for me anymore. I dont want to be creative 48 hrs a week. I want to save it for myself, im selfish. Im jaded. This art game is ugly.

How can there be soo much ugliness in sometihng so beautiful?

So what do i do? I dont know. For some reason i cant sit still. Since ive moved form sac i have not been in a living situation for more than a year and a half. And ive been in la for almost 4 years. I need new. I need a new job. A new country. A new city. A new place. A new life. A new struggle.

I feel like ive been in this 3 year relationship and ive only been in it for so long because i got comfy and its easy. But now she wants to get married and now im not sure if shes right for me. We shouldnt break up but we should have some time apart. Cuz i love her but i want to see what else is out there. And now shes all crying and i feel bad and like a jerk for leaving... Yea kinda like that.

Well graphic design im leaving you. Some day. Its not you its me. We can still be friends ok?

I think i want to be a mechanic.

god damn, i love it when you can find a song that fits your life like a glove
holy shit. dreams do come true! reach for the stars people FUCKIN REACH!

if the only thing you do is run away from your problems, running is the only thing you will be capable of.

don't run, dig your heals into the ground and brace for impact. 

not matter what your mind might tell you, there is always a way to fix what is broken.

so lets all stop being pathetic and start fucking shit up.

see you at the top. *salute*

i lose my the gate remote for the company parking lot, shortly after that i lose the keys to get into the office.

on the other hand, i get a phat raise and i hook up with one of my biggest crushes at the office.

what the hell are these situations tryin to tell me?

this case blows my pervious theory of karma out of the water.

mainly cuz all the happenings in my life are work related...

the only thing i have out side of work is kiwi, tv and xbox.

whats the next move i should make?

is there such a thing as too much good stuff?

am i going to have another major change on my hands?

shit... only the future knows...

THIS GUY! WTF MAN! GROSS COLORD HAT? KABBA MODERN T SHIRT? PLEASE GET THE FUCK OUT! please philippino people get it the fuck together! all hope is lost. we must teach our young that this is not acceptable.

asked the boss to the employee.

i think im going to get another raise soon, yippie! 

its gunna be a good year.

i just got home from work. im doing a collaboration with Ernesto Yerena (look em up) its gunna be fuckin iller than a killer watching thriller. 

i figured something out today.

if you want something, like really want something... you need to fucking take it. fuck the rest.

fuck all this wishing bullshit.

if your not hungry your not going to eat.

and if u dont eat... u die. and im tooo young too die.

and fyi no more hand outs from me. im done being "i feel sorry for you" clean up crew guy.

i have a fine tolerance for slackers.

2009 is gunna crack off.

surround your self with people that will help you. itll be better for every one.

btw... ive been watching alot if The Office and the more i watch it the more my life becomes a sitcom.

i started at season 4 and im working my way back.

i figured im a cross between jim, dwight and toby.

that is all... have a good morning.

fair well 

to you my frieeennd

soo long

fair well

intill we meeeeet again!

p.s.
good riddance

karma karma karma.... why must u punish me?

wait what?!

is my thrusday night fucked up already?.... its only tuesday!

u have got to be fucking kidding me... 

say it aint soo... bradly... from work... is comming too? am i gunna have to pick him up from the airport as well?! 

im bout to blow a gasket 

this really cant be happening... this is a sick joke right? am i being punk'd? 

throw me a frickin bone here. 

what the flying fuck am i doing wrong?

this is where anticipation turns into fear.

last time i checked that wasnt a virtu

i feel like i need to keep track of everything for other people.
or else no one will no what to do with themselves.

too bad i dont need to do that and people need to figure things out on their own.

o yea? o yea! i guess im a bad guy. i mean... i do have a decepticon emblem tattooed on my fore arm... moving on... u never know how much dog shit is actually laying on a side walk till you have a dog. i mean my god theres a lot of dog shit in my neighborhood. but for you that arnt in the know i did get a 4 month old puppy. and her name is kiwi. i really feel like a single parent. just call me the dog father. i rescued her from my friend that was going to put her in the pound... i couldnt let a pup like hers go. she still needs some potty lessons but she is getting there. i mean she shits like 5 times a day. she poops in my room somtimes. bout how can u get mad at a face like that? love of my life. DAMMINT.... during the writing of this post... my fuckin dog peed all over my roommate AND thhe couch he was sitting in... baaad dog... shes out on the porch now for a time out. anyways... she still cute as hell.

so.

i didn't think you still read this journal.

hey. you.... yea. you.

im sorry.

that was pretty fucked of me.

but cant a brother juss vent.

sure sure i know an explanation is in order.

what else can i say other than: "ive been awkward"

cuz for some reason im missing the part of my brain that cant even have a regular conversation with you.

sorry for talking shit, and being a hater.

maybe i really should think before i speak.

i just kinda think your being a kiss ass, brown noser, suck up with that painting...
and i dont see the integrity in that... maybe i was juss expecting too much?
 
i mean... what happen to the dope floral shit?

soo IM thinking YOUR thinking..." hey i know what shep might like! a led zeppelin painting! i bet hell buy it! he looooves led, didnt he juss do their album cover?"
then im thinking... WOWOW losssser...

correct me it im wrong here.. and if i am i just another worthless dick. 

forgive me.

it could of totally been out of coincidence and im just reading to deeeeeply into it,

now i prolly sound like the loser. but hey. the cats out of the bag now. 

think of me what u will.

but i really do think its a nice painting and i hope it sells.

friends still?  i really am embarrassed and sorry... this is kinda awkward u know...

um... see u tomorrow??

and fair thee well internet, i wish to you a goodnight.

how low will you go?

this is just fuckin sad....

ignorance is bliss i suppose.

my 6 months is up and i need to pay off my student loans.

and o boy let me tell you it aint pretty... im in the hole A LOT A LOT A LOT. and on my salary i cant hang.

and whats even worse is im late a few days for my first payment... im feeling a reprimand coming swiftly.

also i manned up and asked mommy for A LOT A LOT A LOT of help. pride, at this point isnt in my vocabulary.

damnit... i havent even left my house yet im feeling the crunch soo bad... rent is due. loan payment is due and thats pretty much my whole months paycheck out the door right there.

here comes the shift. preparations are in order... eating will soon become a luxury 

hahaha.... im fucked.

i need that check from my art show badly.
i need a raise.

old flames reignited? 

3 day trips to la?....

uh oh.

last weekend seems like a blur.

seeing the fam bam was fuckin great. everything i thott it was going to be. helllla refreshing. it was soooo good to see everybody cant wait till the next "reunion"

but see.
i got a chance to hang out with reychelle again. and fuck did i miss her. i know it seems dumb, going after her again... but there is something about what we have that i find really awesome. anyways. she see it too.
we got to talking and we both admitted some pretty heavy stuff, that too was refreshing.
i basically said that ive always had her in the back of my mind and that i just still like her.

her kiss at the end of the night told me "ditto"...

she even dropped me off at the airport.
fitting, cuz ill be picking her up from one soon.
i dont know how i should take this: with a grain of salt, or a spoon full of sugar...
w/e im content with just letting it ride.

i just want to know how this will play out with my whole theory on karma.
i do know that i will be talking the friday off for her when i really shouldnt.
the scales could be tipping sooner than expected...

let me attempt to explain to u the facts of my life.

i have 2 sets of karma: social and professional...

social deals with all things... social. wether it be friends, family, lovers.

professional, deals with the amount of tangible success in my life.

and i believe that these two are linked and share the same pool of good and bad karma.

with that being said...

ill always have money in my pocket, but be socially awkward.

ill be broke with no place to stay, but have friends willing to lend a helping hand...

fallow?

so as of right now. all my good karma is on my professional side.

good ass job. nice ass house. sold out show. fuck yea...

so in turn my social karma must suffer for my success.

im only basing this on the fact that i have sacrificed a lot to be as successful as i am today. i have also done everything by the book and i have paid my dues. i was selfless for the act of my success. i juggled a full class schedule and 2 internships for 6 months. worked as an intern for my current job for a year and a half.

so that explains why i have the best job ever and moved into the nicest house i have ever lived in and pay almost nothing for rent.

on a social level im a complete dick. i have done many fucked up things in my life that i am not proud of, nor do i wish to share and will probably take those actions to the grave. i have self sabotaged relationships because i was to afraid to share my true feelings. ive done many people dirty. 

soo that explains why im soo fuckin awkward, really bad mood swings and my inability to be datable.

so since they share from the same karma pool, i cant have 100% good/bad karma for both.

and thats were the problem is. i need to find a medium. i need balance. 

the only way i think it can work is if i dick people over professionally. which will cause a chain reaction for me to rely on my social karma, which if im correct will lead in doing more positive "social things" THUS regaining balance and becoming well rounded and generally happier.
easier said than done.

thee end.

... that was just a lil peek into my thott process.
the 2 greatest people in the world.

art show this weekend.

first real show that i can make some real money from. im very excited/nervous/anxious.

and im done with everything. all 15 pieces, signed and accounted for. i even went as far to frame the cardboard/paper pieces by sandwiching it between plexiglass and having metal bolts hold it all in place. 

it looks effin sweet. ill have pics up soon

O. and i went out on a date with a girl 8 years older then me, ginger. we went gallery hopping, first to burgamont station in santa monica, then han cholo and another show in echo park. then we had a late night mediterranean dinner at gabby's. good vibes, good company but no kiss at the end. i think she thinks im too young. lol i dont blame her. but it would be nice to hang out again.

one more week till i get paid. and i am in desperate need of some cash. i put a lot of money into this show... im effin penny pinchin over here. ill have to start bringing my lunch to work.

bah. mondays... soo wak. time cards due also... fuck haha.

day one.

im mad stressed. soo much to do. soo little time. i wish i had a personal assistant, that would make life a lil less hectic.

must... keep... up...

moral of the story is...

better days? or! hellish nights?

my inability to find a suitable girlfriend has left me pissed off and bitter.

first off. all i really want is steady sex. secondly and most importantly i just want someone to watch tv with. is that really to much to ask?

correct me if im wrong but i think im a handsome, charming young man with a bright future and a lot to offer.

right? maybe? sorta? kinda? juss a lil bit?

i know about the whole "once u meet her ull know" or the "stop looking and ull find her" bullshit. believe me. it doesnt work. not at the pace im going. fuck all that. 

maybe i should stop being soo picky and just wife the first girl that laughs at my stupid jokes. maybe i should have my grandma find me a hot nursing student in the philippines whos looking for a green card (she is currently on vacation there). MAYBE i should resort to online dating...! i have no idea.

point is. im tired of going stag to events, im tired of going to bed alone, im tired of only cooking for one. im tired of having the only hand i can hold be my own. and im sure as hell tired of youporn.com

so i ask again, but with vigor, what the flying fuckity fuck is wrong with me?

and fuck any girl that calls me dude or man or fool cuz than i know there is not a chance in hell for me. FUCK

if i could be any fruit rite now id be a fuckin lemon. because im sour, soo sour that i could make ur lips pucker soo hard that ur whole face would inverse on itself causing a fatal death... by sourness.

i really have to stop caring. but i cant. i was raised to be a hopeless romantic, this chivalrous knight in shining armor that would sweep a girl off her feet cuz thats what she wanted.

 but thats definitely not the case cuz im sitting here on my day off ranting about my inadequacy with women.

if i had a dime for every failed relationship ive been in id be... well id have 30cents. but thats not the point.

the day I bring back a girl to lumbang family christmas is the day hell freezes over.

nuff said.
wishes do come true.

i need a vacation.

maybe i wanna go home.

lets go back to the suburbs.

i registered to vote today. 

being a part of history really has its draws.

btw im voting donkey.

better late than never.
i get paid on friday. that is all.

its the sensation you get right before you reach the first drop on a roller-coaster... not really sure how else to describe it but its kinda like that.

somethings in the air. 
gotta find out what.

thrilling news.
i finished my last piece for thee art show. 15 done. whew.
maybe thats what it is.

i have the biggest fuckin pimple, dead center of my nose. dead center. 

cheers!
a preview of my art show in september!!! GAH!!! very exciting.

the new intern is horrible, and he was referred by an old employee. conspiracy? lol prolly not.

but gah! there is nothing worse than tryin to train someone that doesnt listen, doesnt fallow directions, and doesnt know how to pentool. whats even worse is that this fool is 35 years old. he should already know whats up. and how to handle his.

ill tell him how to do stuff quicker, and more efficient. "sure" he says. and wen i check up on him his doing his own thing. that takes 3x as long and looks 5x as ugly. 

like wen building a repeatable pattern you only have to build 1/4 of the image. then copy reflect twice (horizontal then vertical), butt up the quarters together to get the initial repeat. then u step repeat. fuckin simple. my lil 4 year old niece can do that.

instead. he rather try to build the whole thing in one shot. its juss common sense. u dont do that.

i try to give him tips... he shoves it back in my face.

ive already expressed this to the boss man... and we both decided to give him a week. but honestly i want him out.

we cant use him. hes useless.

i can talk shit because i never, ever made the mistakes he did. i believe that my job is simple and that anyone can do it. but now im starting to think otherwise.

god help this 35 year old freelance graphic designer because hes really really really  needs it.

i really am a nice guy, but when i work and ur slowing me down its game over. i dont have the tolerance for this micky mouse bullshit. we are short one man, and ill be damned if that guy fills the position.

im sticking my head out for a person that i dont think would do the same and of course its for a girl *sigh* and not just any girl thee girl. the girl ive had a crush on for 3 years now. its sad really. im emotionally invested in someone that doesnt feel the same way. sad sad sad. whats even sadder is that i know its sad, but i continue to mush on relentlessly. 

im tryin to get this girl a job at the studio... O WOW... bad idea. i know its a bad idea. but it seems like a good idea for her. right now thats all that matters too me. if its good for her, if it will make her happy.

i really dont know whats wrong with me. ill keep telling myself i have this unconditional love for her. that my crush has transcended all physical and vocal forms of affection and manifested its self into its own entity. 

sometimes i cant believe the bull shit i think up.

but shes dyeing out there, all she ever talks about is how sad she is where she is, no one will hire her. is it really sad and stupid that im trying to help her out?

i dont know, its really a tug of war between ideals right now.

in one hand, i get her the job and shes lives happily ever after 

in the other hand, i get her the job and now i work with her; further torturing myself to the suppressed feeling i have for her.

this is baaad. why cant i man up and do something about it? a good question indeed.

im fuckin lost, i have no idea what i need to do.
woe is me.

half the line is designed by urs truly.

drop it like its hot.

im moving to my new place. ill be about 5 mins from work. hollar back.

"and the pieces are slowing coming together"
and your wish is my command.

how many different places can phil possibly move into?

"Lets find out...ah-1, ah-2, ah-3, *crunch*... ah-3"

and hes back in the game mother fuckers.

and for all u NOT in the know.... that was a totsie roll pop commercial reference.

a person is most venerable when everything is going their way.

ive learned that today. its true you cant have it all

im always left out, never invited. hard to remember, easy to forget.

for instance. jp decided to go house hunting with out me and the 3 people i was suppose to move in with are just going to be the 3 people minus phil. when he told me i said "o yea? thats kool"  BUT ITS NOT. fuck man. that shit really makes me sad. i mean it was only a 3 bed room place. couldnt they of looked for a 4 bedroom? and this was really the only thing i was looking forward too all year. 

this is the part where i get really insecure about myself and start to question everything i do. ill ask myself if im even a likable guy... am i juss stupid? am i not fun to be around? how come no one calls me to hang out? do i have nothing to offer?

its the worst feeling ever. i dont understand what im doing wrong. maybe i am just a dick?

in any case im sad and this sucks. 

livejournal, your my only friend.='(
